Usage: writeIntegRouteConstraint [-help] -file <string> [-net <net_name> | -name <string> | -additional ]

-help                    # Prints out the command usage
-additional              # This option returns path to additionalConstraint
                         # file. (bool, optional)
-file <string>           # Specifies output constraint file name
                         # (string, required)
-name <string>           # This option returns a specific constraint by name.
                         # (string, optional)
-net <net_name>          # Indicates the net for which the constraints will be
                         # returned. If the net part of a netClass, the
                         # netClass will be returned. (string, optional)